{"tid":544450,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得邊代pokemon最好玩？","createTime":"2018-01-29T13:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T15:18:04.000Z","uid":102978,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"6d29d32c885b197305d038e7d04266b03e114f69","tid":544450,"uid":102978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"Pokemon不知不覺都出左好多年<br />\n轉眼間已經出到第7世代<br />\n<br />\n巴絲覺得邊隻版本最好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我就覺得心金/銀魂最好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n首先有情懷成份,劇情同初代接軌,見到大木博士,Red,Green<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n耐玩性高,有成都關都2幅地圖,16個道館慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊map Gym BGM好熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n精靈數量適中,雖然代代都係用251內既精靈,除非冇得捉..<br />\n<br />\n大家又覺得邊代最好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1b3a521edb20030d294c904e77cf25ffd01823","tid":544450,"uid":116530,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:55:23.000Z","msg":"火紅/葉綠"},{"pid":"5ad4ef21d50c44329f75af0579c9a3cb513b3cec","tid":544450,"uid":71694,"like":3,"dislike":54,"score":-51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d1a38169637c0745d8ffcbdf6908967e9d2e387","tid":544450,"uid":186,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:56:15.000Z","msg":"Show Blocked User - Bincma"},{"pid":"b7868091c00fec5a131ed90427fb8e0c551f9502","tid":544450,"uid":115082,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:56:40.000Z","msg":"金銀"},{"pid":"01c8635ac2d8e531d661e21504c5991353184107","tid":544450,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ea1b3a521edb20030d294c904e77cf25ffd01823","tid":544450,"uid":116530,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T13:55:23.000Z","ms