-29T14:23:39.000Z","msg":"心金魂銀<br />\n樓主講漏左尾隨系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n紅藍寶石復刻有復刻光環再加二周目劇情同d動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n神獸又mega 左樣同能力都勁型棍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得坐Kyogre 巨牙鯊 吼吼鯨游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又有得渣飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日月終於唔駛交通工具同劇情都幾可取<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但點解又取消返飛行環節無得<br />\n不過考驗同跳舞唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事劇情黑白最正<br />\n但寵真係太柒<br />\n柒得黎唔似pkm<br />\n我當自己收服緊數碼精靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總結 寶石復刻＞＞心金銀魂 ＞黑白＞日月＞all"},{"pid":"9b1f5cf4e92d37b879e50ce04fcdac809366de74","tid":544450,"uid":3080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T14:28:06.000Z","msg":"一定係金銀啦,好耐玩,之後再玩返都唔悶<br />\n第一次玩淨係溜冰過第八關個隧道已經用咗幾日時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5dfcdb22adf48e370ef2d3eec686300957ce6d9","tid":544450,"uid":59737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T14:28:15.000Z","msg":"XY 最好玩"},{"pid":"c827c02575065318af565fdcb7bfe93c4eec05cb","tid":544450,"uid":62133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"53add015d45e8a4654661a070de4b487ff945d4f","tid":544450,"uid":34243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"649c6f4d035e3afcc76c5ad7f0e6da6638a5c71a","tid":544450,"uid":16877